author: dblevins
msg: Small hack for getting a global JNDI remotely accessible.  Since each app has an "app scoped" global jndi and we don't have a real global JNDI this lookup technique will not work if there is more than one app in the system.
Once we get an actual global jndi, this same technique can be used, just with lookups going against the real global context
